- cs.IT (Information Theory) is a possibility as the paper mentions the use of entropy in the analysis of syntactic complexity. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possibility as regular languages are often studied in the context of logic and automata theory. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is a possibility as the paper deals with the complexity of regular languages.
